      "description": "FEA-predicted construct stiffness compared against N=11 experimental measurements. Mean experimental stiffness 187.4 N/mm (SD 12.1 N/mm); FEA ensemble mean 191.2 N/mm. Percentage difference 2.0%, well within the 10% acceptance bound. E/uval ratio 0.61, below the 1.96 threshold. Aleatory uncertainty arising from specimen-to-specimen variability is acknowledged in the experimental SD; however, no formal UQ artifact has been linked to characterize the distribution of this variability or propagate it through the model.",
