      "description": "FEA-predicted yield force compared against experimental yield force measurements across N=11 constructs. Mean experimental yield force 412.8 N (SD 18.6 N); FEA ensemble mean 421.5 N. Percentage difference 2.1%, within the 10% acceptance bound. E/uval ratio 0.88. Aleatory scatter in yield force attributable to material lot variation and assembly torque variability is discussed qualitatively in the test report but is not formally characterized via a linked uncertainty quantification record.",
