      "description": "FEA-predicted force at 40 mm crosshead displacement compared against experimental results. Mean experimental force 523.3 N (SD 24.7 N); FEA ensemble mean 537.9 N. Percentage difference 2.8%, within the 10% acceptance bound. E/uval ratio 1.12, below the 1.96 threshold. Uncertainty in large-displacement contact conditions introduces aleatory variability that is acknowledged in prose but not formally propagated through a Monte Carlo or equivalent UQ framework.",
